OL,12,GFor over 100 years now, being able to
OL,13,Gtake an image of brain activity has
OL,14,Gbeen a really useful approach to
OL,15,Gunderstanding how brains work. But,
OL,16,Gmore recently, we’ve learnt how to
OL,17,Gchange brain states. Non-invasive
OL,18,GBrain Stimulation (NiBS) does just
OL,19,Gthat; temporarily interfere with
OL,20,Gnormal brain activation without having
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
